"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-12-No-room-for-anti-doping-double-standards-at-Olympics-or-other-events-1w0jCl7M9QQ-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN Radio  Copied  While athletes put up amazing performances at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics, addressing the issue of doping that is always a threat to undermine the integrity of the prestigious competition is crucial. In this episode, we touch on the controversies over the case in which the United States Anti-Doping Agency (USADA) allegedly allowed athletes who tested positive for banned substances to compete at past editions of the Olympics and other events without facing proper sanctions, while launching criticism over the food contamination incident involving Chinese swimmers. In addition, we talk about the breakthrough performances of Chinese Olympians in Paris and memorable moments at the Games.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"